  "texts": [
    "IntroductionGeneral-purpose vision and language models, particularly those trained on large-scale datasets, show remarkable adaptability to a wide range of downstream tasks [23,31].",
    "However, individually fine-tuning all parameters of these models for every downstream task poses significant efficiency challenges.",
    "This approach becomes increasingly inefficient as the number of tasks grows, especially in envi-* The first two authors contributed equally to this work.",
    "1 https://github.com/scale-lab/MTLoRA.git 10 8 6 4 2 0 2Relative Improvement to Single-Task Fine Tuning (%) ronments constrained by computational resources.",
    "Therefore, there is a need to develop resource-efficient fine-tuning techniques [13,14,22,24]."
  ]
}